

to activate the virtual environnement on mac : source .venv/bin/activate
(on windows: source .venv/Scripts/activate )
to desactivate the virtual environnement on mac : deactivate

to update the requirements.txt: pip  freeze > requirements.txt

pip install -r requirements.txt

Local deploy
to run the server run : python3 APP/GUI_StockForcaster.py
 in if __name__=="__main__":: app.run(host="0.0.0.0", port=8000, _quiet=False)
to stop the server: ctrl+C


to deploy the web app: https://dashboard.render.com/
#to deply on render live web
serve(app, host="0.0.0.0", port=8080, _quiet=False)

    